---
layout: layouts/base.njk
permalink: /india/authors/
title: "India Financial Experts & Authors – CalcPhi"
description: "Meet CalcPhi's India editorial team — CFA charterholders, ICAI Chartered Accountants, and CFPs who verify every India calculator formula and write our financial guides."
breadcrumbs:
  - name: Home
    url: /
  - name: India
    url: /india/
  - name: Our Authors
---

<main id="main-content">

  <div class="authors-page-header">
    <div class="authors-page-header__inner">
      <p class="authors-page-header__eyebrow">India Editorial Team</p>
      <h1>India Financial Experts</h1>
      <p class="authors-page-header__sub">Every India calculator and article on CalcPhi is written and independently verified by a qualified Indian financial professional — CFA, CA, or CFP — with direct knowledge of SEBI, CBDT, AMFI, PFRDA, and RBI regulations.</p>

      <div class="authors-trust-bar">
        <div class="authors-trust-badge">
          <span class="authors-trust-badge__icon">◆</span>
          CFA Institute
        </div>
        <div class="authors-trust-badge">
          <span class="authors-trust-badge__icon">◆</span>
          ICAI Certified CA
        </div>
        <div class="authors-trust-badge">
          <span class="authors-trust-badge__icon">◆</span>
          CFP Board
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="authors-list-wrap">
    <div class="authors-list">
      {% for key, author in authors %}
      {% if author.market == "india" %}
      <article class="author-row">
        <a href="{{ author.url }}" class="author-row__photo-link">
          {% authorImage author.image, author.name + ", " + author.title + " at CalcPhi", 160, "author-row__photo", "lazy" %}
          <span class="author-row__cred-badge">{{ author.credentials }}</span>
        </a>
        <div class="author-row__content">
          <div class="author-row__header">
            <div class="author-row__identity">
              <h2><a href="{{ author.url }}">{{ author.name }}</a><svg class="verified-badge" aria-label="Verified author" title="Verified" viewBox="0 0 20 20" width="18" height="18" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><circle cx="10" cy="10" r="10" fill="#1d9bf0"/><path d="M6 10.5l2.5 2.5L14 7.5" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></h2>
              <p class="author-row__title">{{ author.title }}</p>
            </div>
            <a href="{{ author.url }}" class="author-row__btn">View Profile →</a>
          </div>
          <p class="author-row__bio">{{ author.shortBio }}</p>
          <div class="author-row__footer">
            <div class="author-row__tags">
              {% for skill in author.expertise | slice(0, 4) %}
              <span class="author-row__tag">{{ skill }}</span>
              {% endfor %}
            </div>
            <div class="author-row__articles-count">
              <span>{{ author.articles | length }} article{% if author.articles | length != 1 %}s{% endif %} published</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
      {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="editorial-pledge">
    <div class="editorial-pledge__inner">
      <div class="editorial-pledge__heading">
        <p class="authors-page-header__eyebrow">Our Standards</p>
        <h2>The CalcPhi India Editorial Pledge</h2>
        <p>Every formula and regulatory figure is cross-checked against CBDT notifications, AMFI data, RBI circulars, PFRDA guidelines, or SEBI publications. Rates are updated within 7 days of any official notification.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="editorial-pledge__grid">
        <div class="editorial-pledge__item">
          <span class="editorial-pledge__num">01</span>
          <h3>SEBI & CBDT Verified</h3>
          <p>All investment and tax content is verified against current SEBI and CBDT guidelines before publication.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="editorial-pledge__item">
          <span class="editorial-pledge__num">02</span>
          <h3>AMFI & RBI Data</h3>
          <p>Mutual fund return data uses AMFI-published NAVs. FD and interest rate data is sourced from RBI circulars.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="editorial-pledge__item">
          <span class="editorial-pledge__num">03</span>
          <h3>Updated Within 7 Days</h3>
          <p>When tax slabs, interest rates, or scheme rules change, affected pages are updated within 7 days of official notification.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="editorial-pledge__item">
          <span class="editorial-pledge__num">04</span>
          <h3>Editorial Independence</h3>
          <p>No calculator result or recommendation is influenced by advertising or affiliate relationships. Accuracy only.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="authors-bottom-cta">
    <div class="authors-bottom-cta__inner">
      <p>Looking for our Australia financial experts?</p>
      <a href="/australia/authors/" class="cta-link">Meet the Australia Team →</a>
    </div>
  </div>

</main>
